name: Queen Lux Cozy | 1 min to Subway + 12 min Downtown
neighborhood_overview: We are located 1 min walk from Public Transportation. Bakeries, coffee shops restaurants and ice cream parlor. Short Uber ride to SouthBay shopping center Starbucks and several other restaurants.
description:
Large 4 bedroom unit offering this Spacious room with queen size bed. Share 2 large nicely done bathrooms, kitchen and living room with 1 min walk to MBTA. Bakeries, coffee shops ice cream and many restaurants in the area.

The space
The unit is very large with 4 bedrooms in total. Access a fully stocked kitchen (shared) with everything you will need. 2 very large shared bathrooms, shared living room and WiFi ready.

Guest access
Access to kitchen, 2 bathrooms and large living room with desk and WIFI

Other things to note
ON street Parking is LIMITED if you DRIVE private parking may be an additional $10 a day so please reserve during busy season.
